items.title: Goat cheese bites with marinated sesame seeds
items.description: Marinated sesame seeds are an ideal flavor enhancer. We love them with goat cheese — a creamy and crunchy flavor combination! These low-carb goat cheese bites with marinated sesame seeds will sure be a hit with your guests.

items.title: Keto spinach and goat cheese pie
items.description: There’s good pie, and then there’s mind-blowingly amazing pie. This keto pie falls in the latter category. Savory spinach. Creamy goat cheese. Stunning colors. O.M.G., you want this on your plate!
